{"id":945800084,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"1 week, 1 day","timestamp":1683428577,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"80 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/945800084/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Find the Distinct Difference Array","memory":"93.6 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    vector<int> distinctDifferenceArray(vector<int>& nums) {\n        int n = nums.size();\n        vector<int> ans;\n        unordered_map<int, int> um;\n        vector<int> numn(n, 0);\n        vector<int> numm(n, 0);\n        int count = 0;\n        for(int i=n-1; i>=0; i--){\n            if(um[nums[i]]){\n                numn[i] = count;\n                continue;\n            }\n            count++;\n            numn[i] = count;\n            um[nums[i]] = 1;\n        }\n        um.clear();\n        count = 0;\n        for(int i=0; i<n; i++){\n            if(um[nums[i]]){\n                numm[i] = count;\n                continue;\n            }\n            count++;\n            numm[i] = count;\n            um[nums[i]] = 1;\n        }\n\n        for(int i=0; i<n-1; i++){\n            ans.push_back(numm[i]-numn[i+1]);\n        }\n        ans.push_back(numm[n-1]);\n        return ans;\n    }\n\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"find-the-distinct-difference-array","has_notes":false}
